author_ssm: Jan Hilley and Megan Hahn Fraser
abstract_ssm: The Seaman Family Papers consist of the personal, business and legal papers of four related families based in Long Island and Dutchess County, New York. The Van Horns and Freemans were united with the Seamans and DeWindts by the marriage of Irmingarde Van Horne Freeman and George Williams Seaman in 1903.
geogname_ssm: New York (N.Y.) -- Social life and customs -- 19th century.
